These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, software-developer, lawyer, mechanic, journalist, manager
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, february, january, june, october, november, december
 1. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the dancer##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the paramedic##1
 6. the dancer is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person who's birthday is in june and the mechanic##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the manager is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the lawyer##1
12. the manager is on the left of the software-developer##1
13. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of reggae##1
14. the journalist is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Job   | mechanic | dancer     | journalist | paramedic | lawyer | manager  | software-developer  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Birthday         | february   | december | june    | january  | october | november | april |

