.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, 7up, water, milk, cola, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, zinnia, tulip, amaryllis, bellflower, marigold
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who growsmarigold##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
14. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
15. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate      | water     | iced-tea  | milk | 7up | mirinda |
