 9. the mexican is the person playing poker##1
10. the american is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person playing domino is the turkish##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing domino and the person playing canasta##2
15. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
