12. the craftsman house is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the gothic-revival house is the game-smoker##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
16. the futuristic house is the chaman-smoker##1

