 9. the person driving the motorbike is the egyptian##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the analyst is the person driving the scooter##1
12. the analyst is the person driving the scooter##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the chef##1
