.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, trance, classical, gospel, country, rock, dubstep
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, woodworking, writing
There are 7 different favourite colors: coral, red, green, light-blue, blood-red, brown, emerald
 1. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 4. the fan of country is between the fan of folk and the fan of trance##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 6. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the fan of folk is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who likes red##1
10. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
14. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
15. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Music-Genre        | classical          | gospel | folk      | country  | trance     | dubstep  | rock |
