11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the mexican is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the canadian##1
14. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
15. the turkish is on the far right##1
16. the dutch is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Nationality   | mexican | spanish      | canadian | german     | brazilian     | dutch   | turkish |
| Hobby       | filmmaking    | chess | woodworking    | cooking | collecting     | baking | board-games |
| Pet        | snake    | goldfish | goat    | rabbit    | guinea-pig | chinchilla | bird |

